channel.title: CVE Feed for Unknown -- Product GTIN (EAN, UPC, ISBN) for WooCommerce
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Unknown -- Product GTIN (EAN, UPC, ISBN) for WooCommerce

item.title: CVE-2023-0068|2024-08-02T04:54:32.606Z -- unknown -- product%20gtin%20%28ean%2C%20upc%2C%20isbn%29%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Product GTIN (EAN, UPC, ISBN) for WooCommerce WordPress plugin through 1.1.1 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
